Print the following pattern for the given number of rows.
Pattern for N = 4

    1
   232
  34543
 4567654
567898765

___________________________________________________________________________

n=int(input())
i=1
while i<=n:
    spaces=1
    while spaces<=n-i:
        print(" ",end="")
        spaces+=1
    j=1
    k=i
    while j<=i:
        print(k,end="")
        k+=1
        j+=1
    j=1
    k=2*i-2
    while j<=i-1:
        print(k,end="")
        k-=1
        j+=1
    print()
    i+=1
